# Multi-source Soil Moisture Product Prediction Fusion Dataset

## Dataset Access

Due to the large file sizes, the raw dataset cannot be uploaded directly to GitHub. Please download it from the link below:

**Dataset Name**: Multi-source Soil Moisture Product Prediction Fusion Dataset

**Download Link**: [https://pan.quark.cn/s/38e3d9e5ba7f](https://pan.quark.cn/s/38e3d9e5ba7f)

## How to Download

1. Click the link above to access the shared page
2. Open with the **Quark App** (夸克APP) to save the files to your own cloud storage


## Notes

- This dataset is hosted on Quark Cloud Drive
- Make sure you have sufficient storage space before saving
- For any issues with the download link, please open an issue in this repository

